                    <span class="author">- Sarah A.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-item premium">
                    <div class="stars">â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…</div>
                    <div class="tag">TOP REVIEW</div>
                    <p>"I love the lounge! Playing snooker after a body massage is the ultimate relaxation."</p>
                    <span class="author">- Emeka V.</span>
                </div>
